\begin_layout Subsubsection
Statechart
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
The system is based on two different modes: The active function and the
 passive function.
 The first is in place when the person is actively using the application
 and its functionality.
 The latter is a background service that runs in order to keep track of
 the position and other information and it attract user's attention when
 a notification is risen.
\end_layout

